To implement the functionality for modifying the quantity of products in the shopping cart and recalculating the total price, we need to:
1. Add an endpoint in the `shopping_cart_controller.py` to handle modifying the quantity of cart items.
2. Ensure the quantity is a positive integer.
3. Automatically recalculate the total price whenever the quantity is modified.

## Final Project Folder Structure:
my_project/
├── backend/
│   ├── models/
│   │   ├── user_model.py
│   │   ├── password_reset_model.py
│   │   ├── product_model.py
│   │   ├── category_model.py
│   │   ├── shopping_cart_model.py
│   ├── views/
│   │   ├── user_view.py
│   ├── controllers/
│   │   ├── user_controller.py
│   │   ├── password_reset_controller.py
│   │   ├── profile_controller.py
│   │   ├── product_controller.py
│   │   ├── category_controller.py
│   │   ├── shopping_cart_controller.py
├── database/
│   ├── schema.sql
├── app.py
├── requirements.txt

